description: Parents could receive an extra 10 hours of subsidised nursery fees paid for by the government.
title: Jersey's nursery education entitlement could be increased
title_page: Jersey's nursery education entitlement could be increased - BBC News
maintext: She said: "This has been an extraordinarily difficult year for many families so I hope that this news of extra support for nursery education will help to ease some of those pressures."
